This paper deals with online scheduling policies for energy harvesting communication systems, which involves information theory (cs.IT), networking (cs.NI), and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also discusses optimization techniques for utility functions, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and mathematical optimization (cs.MA).
